{"lemma":"خَفَقاتٌ","slug":"خَفَقاتٌ","root":"خ.ف.ق","root_slug":"خ-ف-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ف-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11128","n11129"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11128","headword_ar":"خَفْقَةٌ","root":"xfq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single nodding of the head, by reason of drowsiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dozing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see 1, in two places: (Mgh, Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light, sleep."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is said in a trad. respecting Ed-Dejjál [or Antichrist],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxoruju fiY xafoqapK mina Ald~iyni","text_ar":"يَخْرُجُ فِى خَفْقَةٍ مِنَ الدِّينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained as meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He will come forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a time when religion will be drowsy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dozing, by reason of weakness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaY xafoqapN mina All~ayoli","text_ar":"مَضَى خَفْقَةٌ مِنَ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A period"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAEapN","text_ar":"سَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the night passed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) ―         -b3-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sayoru All~ayoli AlxafoqataAni wasayoru Aln~ahaAri","text_ar":"سَيْرُ اللَّيْلِ الخَفْقَتَانِ وَسَيْرُ النَّهَارِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbarodaAni","text_ar":"البَرْدَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[The time of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the journeying of the night is the first part thereof and the last part thereof, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"[that of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the journeying of the day is the morning, between daybreak and sunrise, and the evening, between sunset and nightfall."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n11129","headword_ar":"خِفْقَةٌ","root":"xfq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or, as in the Tekmileh, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xafoqapN","text_ar":"خَفْقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing with which one strikes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beats, such as a thong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strap, or a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dir~ap","text_ar":"دِرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (K, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixofaqapN","text_ar":"مِخْفَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  And the former, (K,) or ↓ the latter, (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A smooth desert in which is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the kind of mirage termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=l","text_ar":"ا=ل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK, K:) so says Lth. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxofaqN","text_ar":"مَخْفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","JK"]}]}}